attachments.title: Scarlett Johansson, Facebook MoneyPenny and Corporate Productivity
attachments.text: “Did you ever see the movie ‘Her’?” Slack Technologies’ founder and CEO Stewart Butterfield asks. Soon, he says, Slack will have similar capabilities.
